labs, scans, reports...

66
00:02:29,317 --> 00:02:30,851
My entire medical odyssey.

67
00:02:33,254 --> 00:02:34,655
Fun.

68
00:02:49,203 --> 00:02:50,771
Set up in the lounge

69
00:02:50,804 --> 00:02:52,015
and get me copies
