70
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:53,374
Claire!

71
00:02:53,407 --> 00:02:55,809
Dash. Oh, my God!

72
00:02:55,843 --> 00:02:56,944
Why are you here?

73
00:02:56,977 --> 00:02:58,712
Uh, you changed your number.

74
00:02:58,746 --> 00:03:01,114
Right. Um, it's a long story.

75
