because of the underlying
damage to your liver and kidney.

85
00:03:36,984 --> 00:03:39,162
We'll need to keep you on a
prolonged course of IV antibiotics.

86
00:03:39,186 --> 00:03:40,988
Hey, you hear that, guys?

87
00:03:41,021 --> 00:03:44,558
Hep C and heroin aren't
as much fun as they sound.

88
00:03:44,592 --> 00:03:46,035
Although one was more fun
than the other...

89
00:03:46,059 --> 00:03:47,127
For a while.

90
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:49,129
Don't they have
somewhere else to go?

91
00:03:49,162 --> 00:03:50,731
Not likely.

92
00:03:50,764 --> 00:03:54,234
